item.title: Find the Joy in the Adventure of Living Alive!
item.description: No matter what I've done, and no matter where I've been in my life, there has always been a deep rooted pull to the mountains in my soul. When I'm out in the wilderness, when I'm standing on the top of a rocky peak, when I'm suspended on the side of a cliff pondering my next move, I am always impacted by the beauty and simplicity of the mountains and being outside. I can't help but think, every time, that this is what the world was meant to be like. Peaceful, beautiful, and begging to be experienced.
